---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Fatawa Library"
  description="Learn what Fatawa Library is, which scholars are represented, and how to contact us."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl text-teal-900 dark:text-gold-400 mb-6">About Fatawa Library</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-fatwa prose-stone dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2>What Fatawa Library Is</h2>
      <p>
        Fatawa Library is a curated library of translated Islamic fatwas, built to help English-speaking readers
        access rulings from trusted scholars with clear links to the original source material.
      </p>

      <h2>Scholars Included</h2>
      <p>
        The library features translations from senior scholars, including well-known scholars from the Salafi
        scholarly tradition. Each entry identifies the issuing scholar and source URL.
      </p>

      <h2>Translation Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        All translations are provided for educational benefit. They may not fully capture every nuance of the
        original Arabic text. For precision and personal religious questions, consult qualified scholars directly.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For corrections or inquiries, contact:
        <a href="mailto:fatawalib@example.com">fatawalib@example.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
